108
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:54,479
from the candle bodies to the tips of

109
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:57,600
the wicks. Completely different story.

110
00:04:54,479 --> 00:05:00,000
Now when price retests this zone, we

111
00:04:57,600 --> 00:05:02,800
