119
00:05:20,880 --> 00:05:27,360
one arbitrary point. And third, it gives

120
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:30,320
you a clear area to define your risk.

121
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:33,600
Your stop-loss doesn't go below a line.

122
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:36,320
it goes below the entire zone. This is

123
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:39,280
one of the biggest yet simplest changes

124
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:42,000
you can make to your trading. Just by

125
00:05:39,280 --> 00:05:45,039
making that one shift, you've eliminated

126
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:47,440
one of the biggest reasons traders miss

127
00:05:45,039 --> 00:05:50,800
or get stopped out of perfect retest

128
00:05:47,440 --> 00:05:53,759
trades. Here's a situation every trader

129
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:56,560
