153
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:59,520
moves higher and falling volume on the

154
00:06:57,919 --> 00:07:02,080
pullbacks.

155
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:04,720
Most traders think all breakouts are the

156
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:07,680
