158
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:12,960
money players know that not all

159
00:07:09,919 --> 00:07:15,280
breakouts are created equal. The amateur

160
00:07:12,960 --> 00:07:18,080
approach is to trade every breakout that

161
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:20,400
