177
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:03,919
strength behind the move. The biggest

178
00:08:01,199 --> 00:08:05,840
mistake traders make with retests is

179
00:08:03,919 --> 00:08:08,479
thinking that a simple touch of the

180
00:08:05,840 --> 00:08:10,720
