227
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:18,240
volume on the engulfing candle. This is

228
00:10:15,279 --> 00:10:20,720
textbook institutional behavior.

229
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:23,440
If the engulfing candle is my favorite

230
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:26,000
