246
00:11:04,959 --> 00:11:10,800
Here's my technique. When I see a pin

247
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:13,920
bar forming at a retest level, I check

248
00:11:10,800 --> 00:11:17,120
two things. First, does the wick clearly

249
00:11:13,920 --> 00:11:20,399
