252
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:29,760
execution is straightforward. I enter at

253
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:32,399
the close of the pin bar. My target is

254
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:35,839
the next major level in the direction of

255
00:11:32,399 --> 00:11:38,560
the breakout. But here's the refinement.

256
00:11:35,839 --> 00:11:41,760
The best pin bars don't just reject from

257
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:44,240
the level. They reject violently. They

258
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:47,279
create a wick that's so dramatic it

259
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:49,360
tells a story. The story is simple.

260
00:11:47,279 --> 00:11:52,399
Smart money tried to push the market

261
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:55,519
