262
00:11:52,399 --> 00:11:58,000
they're going the other way. This is a

263
00:11:55,519 --> 00:12:00,240
rule that separates professional traders

264
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:03,519
from the rest, and it's incredibly

265
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:06,880
simple. Remember this, the first retest

266
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:09,600
is the most important retest. This is my

267
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:12,720
golden rule, and it's based on years of

